1
00:00:14,457 --> 00:00:16,105
UNK

2
00:00:17,494 --> 00:00:19,378
DVENADTSATAYA MAYA

3
00:00:19,418 --> 00:00:21,111
TYSYACHA DEVYAT'SOT

4
00:00:21,111 --> 00:00:23,344
DEVYANOSTO SHESTOGO GODA.

5
00:00:23,788 --> 00:00:27,697
INTERV'YUIRUEMYY: Kasriel Koblents.

6
00:00:28,007 --> 00:00:32,068
INTERV'YUIRUYUSHCHIY: Khaim Bargman.

7
00:00:32,462 --> 00:00:34,138
GOROD: KAUNAS.

8
00:00:34,138 --> 00:00:36,118
STRANA: LITVA.

9
00:00:36,141 --> 00:00:38,143
YAZYK: IDISH.

10
00:00:42,621 --> 00:00:44,643
haynt iz der tsvelfter may

11
00:00:44,643 --> 00:00:47,508
fun toyznt nayn hundert zeks un nayntsiktn yor.

12
00:00:47,515 --> 00:00:53,583
mir gefinen zikh in Lite, in dem tsveytn shtot f- i- in dem tsveytn shtot fun Lite, Kovne.

13
00:00:54,045 --> 00:00:57,380
di intervyu vet gebn Kasriel Koblents.

14
00:00:57,387 --> 00:01:01,030
dem intervyu vet nemen Khaim Bargman.

15
00:01:01,048 --> 00:01:03,877
di, dem intervyu veln mir firn oyf yidish.

16
00:01:07,157 --> 00:01:09,648
ikh, Kasriel Koblents,

17
00:01:09,655 --> 00:01:13,330
bin geborn in toyznt nayn hundert tsvey un tsvantsiktn yor,

18
00:01:13,330 --> 00:01:15,130
dem fuftsetn mart,

19
00:01:15,375 --> 00:01:17,394
in shtot VOLOGDA.

20
00:01:19,290 --> 00:01:22,389
iz vifl yor zayt ir gevorn hayyor dem fuftsetn merts?

21
00:01:22,142 --> 00:01:25,420
 tsvey, dray un zibetsik yor.

22
00:01:32,217 --> 00:01:37,003
un, vi, vos gedenkt ir, di ershte derinerungen fun ayer lebn?

23
00:01:38,207 --> 00:01:42,836
fun ayer lebn, fun mayn lebn gedenk ikh ot vos. nu, ikh'l onfangen fun mayne eltern:

24
00:01:42,836 --> 00:01:44,464
zey hobn zikh evakuirt

25
00:01:44,464 --> 00:01:46,709
fun, shtot Zarasay in

26
00:01:46,709 --> 00:01:49,035
Rusland, di ershte velt-milkhome.

27
00:01:49,125 --> 00:01:51,886
zey hobn zikh bazesn in shtot VOLOGDA,

28
00:01:51,893 --> 00:01:53,929
un dortn bin ikh geborn gevorn.

29
00:01:55,099 --> 00:01:59,365
⟨ts-⟩ nokh di krig zaynen mir gekumen tsu forn tsurik in Lite

30
00:01:59,365 --> 00:02:03,378
un zikh bazesn in shtot Zarasay, dortn vu zey hobn gelebt biz di krig.

31
00:02:04,026 --> 00:02:07,204
mayn foter hot zikh farnumen mit land-virtshaft.

32
00:02:07,204 --> 00:02:09,993
er hot gehat eygene e- gehat land.

33
00:02:10,101 --> 00:02:14,398
nu, undzer familye iz geven zeyer a groyse: UNK zibn kinder

34
00:02:14,455 --> 00:02:16,845
⟨u- un⟩ tate un mame, nayn mentshn.

35
00:02:17,340 --> 00:02:19,494
⟨m- d-⟩ fun derayn hobn mir gelebt;

36
00:02:20,007 --> 00:02:22,127
mir hobn ale gearbet oyf di land.

37
00:02:22,656 --> 00:02:28,600
nu, mir hobn ongefangen zikh lernen, iz, geven der lebn zeyer a shverer geven.

38
00:02:28,600 --> 00:02:30,395
mir flegn fun in der fri

39
00:02:30,655 --> 00:02:35,796
oyfshteyn, flegt men undz avekfirn fir a, zumer, fir a zeyger in der fri avekfirn in feld,

40
00:02:35,987 --> 00:02:38,377
oyf di land, geholfn arbetn.

41
00:02:38,670 --> 00:02:43,417
mir flegn akht a zeyger kumen fun feld in shtub nemen di por bikher

42
00:02:43,417 --> 00:02:44,908
un geyn in klas.

43
00:02:45,370 --> 00:02:49,509
kumendik fun klas flegn mir vider geyn in feld, geholfn di eltern.

44
00:02:49,509 --> 00:02:51,130
azoy hobn mir gelebt

45
00:02:51,130 --> 00:02:53,870
di gantse, gantse yorn tsayt.

46
00:02:54,094 --> 00:02:57,463
vos hot ir konkret geton mit ayere eygene hent oyf di feld?

47
00:02:57,705 --> 00:02:58,846
ale arbet.

48
00:02:59,207 --> 00:03:03,080
ale arbet velkhe s'fodert zikh, oyf land-virtshaft:

49
00:03:03,308 --> 00:03:05,411
gez- ge- gekoshet,

50
00:03:05,468 --> 00:03:11,486
gezeyet, gegrobn bulbes, ale arbet vos me, ⟨er tut oyf⟩ di felder, dos hobn mir geton.

51
00:03:11,391 --> 00:03:14,220
nu, mistome akern hot aykh nit oysgekumen?

52
00:03:14,125 --> 00:03:16,260
nu, ikh bin nokh geven tsu kleyn tsum akern.

53
00:03:16,453 --> 00:03:18,556
der, ayer foter hot gekent akern?

54
00:03:18,276 --> 00:03:19,960
nu, er iz geven a erd-arbeter.

55
00:03:19,997 --> 00:03:21,965
UNK hot er gek- geakert?

56
00:03:21,263 --> 00:03:26,150
geakert, ye, mit a, mit ferd. m- dan iz keyn traktors nit geven, nor mit ferd.

57
00:03:26,629 --> 00:03:29,103
efsher gedenkt ir, vifl erd hot ir gehat?

58
00:03:29,000 --> 00:03:30,470
akht hektar.

59
00:03:31,067 --> 00:03:33,525
dos hot geklekt durkhtsulebn a mishpokhe?

60
00:03:33,379 --> 00:03:35,077
zeyer shver geven,

61
00:03:35,758 --> 00:03:40,830
nor m'hot gelebt zeyer,... ⟨vi me⟩ zogt, ⟨, sh-⟩...

62
00:03:40,011 --> 00:03:41,237
shporevdik.

63
00:03:41,260 --> 00:03:42,030
?

64
00:03:41,648 --> 00:03:43,009
shporevdik.

65
00:03:42,576 --> 00:03:45,580
shporevdik, az s'hot geda- s'hot gemuzt klekn.

66
00:03:45,850 --> 00:03:47,042
s'hot gedarft klekn.

67
00:03:47,875 --> 00:03:50,400
mir hobn gehat tsvey ferd, tsvey ki.

68
00:03:50,406 --> 00:03:53,769
mir hobn gehat eygene milkh, eygene puter, eygene

69
00:03:53,769 --> 00:03:57,313
eyer. hiner iz geven zeyer fil. nu, V OBSHCHEM, a,

70
00:03:57,313 --> 00:04:02,020
a, lebn vi es lebt a land-virtshaft, oyf land-virtshaft a...

71
00:04:03,113 --> 00:04:05,250
 zogt mir aza zakh:,

72
00:04:05,357 --> 00:04:08,186
ayer foter, ayer mishpokhe iz geven a gleybike?

73
00:04:08,293 --> 00:04:10,227
ir flegt bazukhn di kloyz?

74
00:04:09,160 --> 00:04:14,953
 nit keyn fanatiker un nit keyn apikorsim, vi me zogt dos.

75
00:04:15,381 --> 00:04:18,125
a, a eynfakh yidishe familye.

76
00:04:18,300 --> 00:04:21,314
ayer foter flegt bazukhn di kloyz in Zarasay?

77
00:04:20,893 --> 00:04:21,893
ya.

78
00:04:22,080 --> 00:04:25,540
vi oft flegt er dos ton, oder yeder shabes, oder nor oyf yom-...?

79
00:04:24,520 --> 00:04:26,060
yedn shabes.

80
00:04:26,333 --> 00:04:29,310
yedn shabes un yontoyvim.

81
00:04:29,455 --> 00:04:31,356
un a poshetn tog nit?

82
00:04:31,682 --> 00:04:32,975
keyn tsayt nit geven.

83
00:04:33,927 --> 00:04:37,549
ayer mame flegt, bentshn likht, fraytik-tsu-nakht?

84
00:04:36,778 --> 00:04:40,300
bentshn likht, haltn fun yidishkeyt.

85
00:04:41,250 --> 00:04:43,421
der tate flegt zogn kidesh,

86
00:04:43,663 --> 00:04:44,872
makhn kidesh?

87
00:04:43,700 --> 00:04:48,855
ale mol fraytik in ovnt makhn kidesh. mir flegn zikh arumzetsn arum tish, ale kinder.

88
00:04:49,013 --> 00:04:51,251
nu, me fleg makhn kidesh un...

89
00:04:52,675 --> 00:04:54,373
un onheybn dem shabes.

90
00:04:54,107 --> 00:04:55,660
onheybn shabes, ya.

91
00:04:55,223 --> 00:05:00,617
un, bayn endikn shabes, vet, flegt, der foter makhn an havdole? bay aykh iz geven aza zakh?

92
00:04:59,840 --> 00:05:04,500
neyn. m'fleg makhn havdole nor in shul, in besmedresh.

93
00:05:03,930 --> 00:05:06,573
in shtub v- flegt ir keyn havdoles nit makhn?

94
00:05:05,351 --> 00:05:06,830
neyn, neyn.

95
00:05:07,558 --> 00:05:08,952
nor kidesh makhn.

96
00:05:09,014 --> 00:05:12,160
, zogt mir, ir gedenkt,

97
00:05:12,160 --> 00:05:14,522
vu un ven hot ir zikh ongehoybn lernen?

98
00:05:14,899 --> 00:05:17,880
ikh hob zikh ongefangen lernen umgefer in

99
00:05:18,308 --> 00:05:22,450
tsvey un draysikstn yor, bin ikh avek in shul.

100
00:05:22,729 --> 00:05:25,018
zayt ir shoyn geven ⟨nor⟩ elf yor shoyn?

101
00:05:24,855 --> 00:05:27,180
neyn, dos ⟨iz n-⟩ ikh hob a toes.

102
00:05:27,876 --> 00:05:29,720
tsvey un tsvantsik...

103
00:05:29,884 --> 00:05:33,990
nu, mistome in nayn un tsvantsiktn yor

104
00:05:34,542 --> 00:05:37,641
bin ikh avek lernen i- in a yidishe folk-shul,

105
00:05:38,524 --> 00:05:40,990
un dortn hob ikh opgelernt

106
00:05:41,123 --> 00:05:43,990
zeks klasn hob ikh geendikt.

107
00:05:44,498 --> 00:05:48,373
nu, azoy vi di, di, in shtub iz geven di lage zeyer a shvere,

108
00:05:48,801 --> 00:05:50,347
hob ikh gemuzt geyn arbetn.

109
00:05:50,792 --> 00:05:53,280
far mir iz nokh geven tsvey shvester;

110
00:05:53,280 --> 00:05:55,410
ikh bin shoyn geven der driter in familye.

111
00:05:56,344 --> 00:06:02,270
⟨nu,⟩ bin ikh avek arbetn far a shnayder. bay undz iz, ken men zogn, di gantse SEM'YA geven ale fun shnayders, m⟨ir zaynen⟩...

112
00:06:01,170 --> 00:06:03,644
al- di gantse mishpokhe bay aykh iz geven shnay-...

113
00:06:02,640 --> 00:06:07,611
gantse mishpokhe. mir zaynen geven zibn kinder, zaynen geven fir shnayders fun ale zibn kinder.

114
00:06:08,410 --> 00:06:10,761
nu, kh'hob es ongefangen lernen shnayderay

115
00:06:10,761 --> 00:06:14,698
bay zeyer a gutn shnayder ⟨iz er, baym⟩ bestn shnayder in Zarasay.

116
00:06:14,856 --> 00:06:17,265
nu, kh'hob ⟨fun im⟩ gelernt arbetn zeyer gut.

117
00:06:17,265 --> 00:06:20,530
kh'hob opgearbet akht yor in Zarasay bay shnayderay.

118
00:06:20,222 --> 00:06:24,755
ir hot g- ir gedenkt dem nomen un di familye fun dem mentshn velkher hot aykh gelernt shnayderay?

119
00:06:23,895 --> 00:06:25,910
ya, Tsimerman.

120
00:06:26,331 --> 00:06:28,282
UNK der shnayder hot geheysn Tsimerman?

121
00:06:27,350 --> 00:06:29,481
Avrom-Moyshe Tsimerman.

122
00:06:29,284 --> 00:06:31,890
u- er iz geven a sakh elter fun aykh?

123
00:06:31,714 --> 00:06:35,000
o, er iz shoyn geven an alter yid,

124
00:06:35,275 --> 00:06:37,007
shoyn geven iber di zibetsiker.

125
00:06:37,350 --> 00:06:44,516
ir gedenkt efsher, ir hot gedarft tsoln far dem vos ir lernt zikh shnayderay, tsu er hot aykh getsolt far dos vos ir helft im?

126
00:06:43,000 --> 00:06:45,798
nu, s'iz geven azoy dan opgeredt:

127
00:06:46,277 --> 00:06:48,886
di mame iz avek mit mir tsu im,

128
00:06:49,483 --> 00:06:54,067
un, m'hot m⟨UNK⟩, m'hot mir ongenumen far a lern-yingl.

129
00:06:54,259 --> 00:06:58,421
der onfang iz geven azoy: m'hot nit gelernt glaykh lernen neyen.

130
00:06:58,495 --> 00:07:01,543
m'hot gedarft oyskern dem, di, di padloge.

131
00:07:02,123 --> 00:07:06,842
m'hot gedarft geyn in krom, brengen produktn farn balebos.

132
00:07:06,848 --> 00:07:12,326
m'hot gedarft brengen koyln oyf, oyf di presn tsum, heytsn.

133
00:07:12,619 --> 00:07:14,081
dos iz geven di arbet.

134
00:07:14,172 --> 00:07:17,726
nokh dem, az er hot gezen az ikh STARA- az ikh,...

135
00:07:16,872 --> 00:07:19,220
mi zikh. az ir mit zikh.

136
00:07:18,357 --> 00:07:21,087
ikh ⟨hob bamit zikh⟩ zeyer, ⟨mi⟩ zikh zeyer,

137
00:07:21,087 --> 00:07:23,413
dan hot er mir ongefangen lernen shnayderay.

138
00:07:23,419 --> 00:07:25,893
ikh bin geven tsu shnayderay zeyer a feiker.

139
00:07:26,440 --> 00:07:28,914
nu, un ikh hob opgearbet umgefer

140
00:07:29,511 --> 00:07:32,323
a halb yor, hot er mir shoyn genumen tsoln.

141
00:07:32,565 --> 00:07:33,689
genumen tsoln.

142
00:07:34,168 --> 00:07:37,910
nu, s'iz avek nokh a halb yor, hot er mir alts gehekhert di, di,

143
00:07:37,910 --> 00:07:39,681
di, di gelt, un azoy arum

144
00:07:40,210 --> 00:07:42,532
hob ikh opgearbet bay im akht yor.

145
00:07:42,370 --> 00:07:46,819
efsher gedenkt ir di gehaltn velkhe hot ir gekrogn frier un dernokh shpeter?

146
00:07:46,318 --> 00:07:48,894
nu, di gehaltn iz geven,

147
00:07:49,558 --> 00:07:51,870
tsen lit, fuf-...

148
00:07:50,908 --> 00:07:52,016
a khoydesh?

149
00:07:51,870 --> 00:07:54,250
ye. fuftsn lit,...

150
00:07:54,351 --> 00:07:58,513
vos s'iz geven, geven, plus s'iz geven, fleg zayn a CHAY.

151
00:07:58,738 --> 00:08:00,115
a, oyf tey.

152
00:08:00,173 --> 00:08:01,326
oyf tey.

153
00:08:01,326 --> 00:08:05,381
ikh fleg, me flegt oyfneyen, lomir zogn, a kostyum, a mantl, flegt men avektrogn

154
00:08:05,421 --> 00:08:12,418
tsum, tsum, in, vemen es gehert, flegt er farn brengen gebn a lit, gebn fuftsik sent,...

155
00:08:12,728 --> 00:08:19,725
un akhuts aykh un, dem Tsimermanen, zaynen nokh geven shnayderay tsuz- shnayders tsuzamen mit aykh in dem zelbikn varshtat?

156
00:08:18,961 --> 00:08:20,470
geven.

157
00:08:20,271 --> 00:08:22,374
vifl zaynen nokh geven mentshn bay aykh?

158
00:08:22,313 --> 00:08:24,770
nu, s'zaynen geven zeks man.

159
00:08:24,827 --> 00:08:26,480
s'flegt zikh baytn,

160
00:08:26,480 --> 00:08:29,700
umgefer zeks man hot er gehaltn POSTOYANN-, shtendik.

161
00:08:28,776 --> 00:08:30,170
shtendik, ye.

162
00:08:29,710 --> 00:08:31,650
ya. zeks arbeter,

163
00:08:31,650 --> 00:08:33,124
ale gute shnayder.

164
00:08:33,501 --> 00:08:37,832
vifl tsimern iz geven der varshtat? ale zaynen g- za- ale zayt ir gezesn in eyn tsimer?

165
00:08:37,030 --> 00:08:39,638
⟨y- ye⟩. gearbet hot men ⟨mi-⟩ bay im in shtub.

166
00:08:40,082 --> 00:08:41,834
tsvey tsimern hot er gehat:

167
00:08:41,834 --> 00:08:46,210
eyn tsimer iz geven di shnayderay un in tsveytn tsimer hobn zey gelebt.

168
00:08:48,216 --> 00:08:51,028
der Tsimerman iz geven nor mit a tokhter,

169
00:08:51,726 --> 00:08:53,010
zalbe tsveyt.

170
00:08:54,780 --> 00:08:59,144
vos hot ir al- aleyn p- perzenlekh geneyt?, kostyumen, mantlen, hoyzn?

171
00:08:58,864 --> 00:09:01,590
nor menershe zakhn, altseding.

172
00:09:01,615 --> 00:09:03,786
un ir hot aleyn oykhet geneyt mantlen?

173
00:09:03,589 --> 00:09:09,560
ya, alts: mantlen, vinter-peltsn, hoyzn, ⟨s-⟩, zhiletn, altseding.

174
00:09:09,563 --> 00:09:11,632
un ir flegt oykh tsushnaydn aleyn?

175
00:09:11,154 --> 00:09:12,154
neyn.

176
00:09:12,043 --> 00:09:13,505
ver flegt tsushnaydn?

177
00:09:13,060 --> 00:09:15,470
der balebos aleyn, Tsimerman.

178
00:09:15,418 --> 00:09:17,875
a. Tsimerman flegt ts- ale mol tsushnaydn?

179
00:09:16,050 --> 00:09:21,943
ya. dan hot men, di arbeter hobn dan tsushnaydn nit gekent; zey hobn ge- nor gekent neyen.

180
00:09:22,422 --> 00:09:25,430
tsushnaydn, dos iz geven der, dem balebos' arbet.

181
00:09:25,729 --> 00:09:29,840
un azoy hot ir zikh keyn mol nit oysgelernt tsushnaydn, tsu hot, tsu ir hot zikh oysgelernt?

182
00:09:29,340 --> 00:09:30,920
 neyn.

183
00:09:31,095 --> 00:09:32,489
biz hayntikn tog?

184
00:09:31,820 --> 00:09:37,590
s'iz mir nit geven neytik. s'iz, bay mir iz avek der lebn azoy az kh'hob dos nit, geneytikt zikh in derayn.

185
00:09:38,655 --> 00:09:42,412
 b- far vos hot z- ven hot zikh geendikt ayer lebn in Zarasay?

186
00:09:41,980 --> 00:09:47,644
 fun Zarasay bin ikh avekgeforn in nayn un draysikstn yor,

187
00:09:48,932 --> 00:09:51,305
vayle mayne tsvey shvester

188
00:09:51,345 --> 00:09:53,180
hobn shoyn gelebt in Kovne.

189
00:09:53,505 --> 00:09:58,660
in di kleyne shtetlekh iz der yugnt hot nit gevelt zeyer zayn; m'hot untergevaksn,

190
00:09:58,660 --> 00:10:02,091
hot men shoyn gevelt lebn in a gresere shtot, zikh fayn onton

191
00:10:02,091 --> 00:10:08,130
un bazukhn kino, teater, hobn kompanyes. in a kleyne shtetl iz di meglekhkeyt nit geven.

192
00:10:08,592 --> 00:10:13,752
nu, iz hob ikh opgearbet akht yor un in nayn un draysiktn yor bin ikh avekgeforn in Kovne.

193
00:10:13,752 --> 00:10:16,760
zey hobn mir geshribn a briv, di shvester: "kum tsu forn.

194
00:10:16,760 --> 00:10:19,880
mir hobn far dir gekrogn arbet." un azoy hob ikh geton.

195
00:10:19,898 --> 00:10:22,136
vi iz geven di nemen fun ayere shvester?

196
00:10:22,328 --> 00:10:24,054
Tsherne, di eltste.

197
00:10:24,054 --> 00:10:25,950
di tsveyte hot geheysn Ester.

198
00:10:26,597 --> 00:10:30,674
un vayter hob ikh gehat finf brider, finf brider zaynen mir geven. alemen zogn?

199
00:10:30,732 --> 00:10:32,177
yo, ir kent zogn.

200
00:10:32,014 --> 00:10:35,149
nu, ikh bin geven UNK nokh mir iz geven

201
00:10:35,149 --> 00:10:37,475
Mikh- Mikhke, MIKHAIL,

202
00:10:37,735 --> 00:10:39,298
 Meyer,

203
00:10:39,928 --> 00:10:42,650
 Hirshl, Tsodik.

204
00:10:43,270 --> 00:10:45,626
un mer keyn shvester hot ir n- shoyn nit gehat?

205
00:10:44,916 --> 00:10:47,930
tsvey shvester un finf brider zaynen mir geven.

206
00:10:48,147 --> 00:10:53,220
iz, az di shvester hobn ⟨z-⟩ aykh gerufn, hobn zey shoyn far aykh foroysgezen arbet in Kovne?

207
00:10:52,804 --> 00:10:57,408
ye, zey hobn a- gehat ongegreyt frier arbet. anit bin ikh nit geforn, vayle kumen in Kovne

208
00:10:57,408 --> 00:10:59,256
hot gekost zeyer tayer dan,

209
00:10:59,256 --> 00:11:02,276
un kumen do un arumgeyn iber di gasn hob ikh nit gevelt.

210
00:11:02,276 --> 00:11:06,736
hobn zey mir bazorgt arbet; ikh bin gekumen tsu forn un glaykh oyfn tsveytn tog bin ikh avek arbetn.

211
00:11:06,760 --> 00:11:08,543
vos iz dos geven far an arbet?

212
00:11:09,240 --> 00:11:14,161
gearbet hob ikh oyf K⟨ĘSKUCIO b-⟩ oyf KĘSTUČIO gas, bay eynem a shnayder Kremer.

213
00:11:17,307 --> 00:11:19,073
KĘSTUČIO zibn un draysik.

214
00:11:20,293 --> 00:11:22,227
vos hot ir geton bay dem Kremer?

215
00:11:22,030 --> 00:11:25,602
 nu, dortn iz geven a,

216
00:11:26,233 --> 00:11:28,421
yeder hot zikh gehat zayn arbet:

217
00:11:28,849 --> 00:11:33,213
eyner hot gemakht di arbl, der tsveyter hot gemakht di keshenes, der driter hot gemakht...

218
00:11:33,253 --> 00:11:40,014
nu, dos iz geven ayngeshtelt az yeder eyner hot zikh gehat zayn arbet, un s'flegt gikher aroyskumen di, di fartike...

219
00:11:40,611 --> 00:11:44,503
vos hot geneyt, Kremer's varshtat? oykhet k- menershe zakhn?

220
00:11:45,015 --> 00:11:48,040
⟨oy-⟩ oykh nor menershe zakhn, vayl...

221
00:11:47,040 --> 00:11:49,228
un mantlen hot er shoyn oykh geneyt?

222
00:11:49,251 --> 00:11:52,930
mantlen, iz, zeyer veynik.

223
00:11:52,950 --> 00:11:56,680
nor kostyumen flegt er neyen, merstn teyl kostyumen.

224
00:11:56,642 --> 00:11:59,977
un vos iz geven ayer perzenlekhe arbet bay Kremern?

225
00:11:59,815 --> 00:12:06,933
ikh fleg keshenes makhn, araynlozn keshenes, krages opleygn, araynshteln arbl. nu, kh'hob gehat, V OBSHCHEM,

226
00:12:06,933 --> 00:12:09,490
vi me zogt, ⟨zi iz⟩ di hekhste

227
00:12:10,598 --> 00:12:12,390
madreyge tsu...

228
00:12:11,577 --> 00:12:15,503
dos iz geven a, dos iz, bay di shnayder rekhnt zikh a, di hekhste madreyge, az...?

229
00:12:14,508 --> 00:12:16,240
ya, ⟨KO-⟩ UNK vi den?

230
00:12:15,880 --> 00:12:17,450
araynlozn an ar⟨b-...⟩?

231
00:12:16,504 --> 00:12:20,227
s'fangt zikh on fun a lern-yingl biz di hekhste madreyge.

232
00:12:20,757 --> 00:12:23,788
aha. un araynlozn arbl, dos iz, rekhnt zikh shoyn UNK...?

233
00:12:22,815 --> 00:12:27,720
dos iz, dos rekhnt zikh shoyn di he- di UNK vikhtikste arbet ⟨iz⟩ araynshteln arbl.

234
00:12:27,810 --> 00:12:31,381
efsher gedenkt ir vifl Kremer flegt aykh tsoln far aza arbet?

235
00:12:32,130 --> 00:12:35,769
nu, ikh bin b- dortn geven ba⟨tsolt⟩ nit nor far di arbet.

236
00:12:36,012 --> 00:12:38,210
mir flegn yedn vokh bakumen

237
00:12:38,210 --> 00:12:39,700
draysik lit,

238
00:12:39,700 --> 00:12:43,080
finf un draysik lit; vifl mer arbet me hot gemakht,

239
00:12:43,080 --> 00:12:45,390
azoy flegt er farteyln far di arbeter.

240
00:12:46,068 --> 00:12:47,068
..

241
00:12:46,137 --> 00:12:47,852
fardint zeyer gut.

242
00:12:48,955 --> 00:12:50,352
gehat a, ikh bin geven,

243
00:12:50,352 --> 00:12:55,614
kh'hob gehat, gedungen a tsimer mit nokh eynem oyf, oyf KALVIŲ gas.

244
00:12:55,907 --> 00:13:00,150
un, ⟨un kh'bin geven⟩ zeyer tsufridn fun di arbet, fun, fun altseding.

245
00:12:59,923 --> 00:13:02,870
efsher gedenkt ir, mit vemen hot ir gelebt tsuzamen in a tsimer?

246
00:13:02,843 --> 00:13:04,552
er iz geven,

247
00:13:04,552 --> 00:13:06,093
a Utyaner,

248
00:13:07,062 --> 00:13:09,266
Bentsl, Bentsl...

249
00:13:10,318 --> 00:13:12,840
zeyger-makher; familye hob ikh shoyn fargesn.

250
00:13:12,985 --> 00:13:15,831
a. er iz aleyn geven a z⟨eyn⟩ger- a zeyger-makher?

251
00:13:15,140 --> 00:13:16,740
a zeyger-makher, ya.

252
00:13:18,553 --> 00:13:24,402
un, vifl hot ir getsolt farn tsimer, gedenkt ir efsher? vifl hot dos gekost tsimer-...?

253
00:13:23,532 --> 00:13:26,175
der tsimer hot undz tayer nit gekost.

254
00:13:26,198 --> 00:13:30,326
mir flegn tsoln, beyde flegn mir tsoln tsu tsvantsik lit a monat,

255
00:13:30,467 --> 00:13:31,700
iz fertsik lit.

256
00:13:32,408 --> 00:13:34,764
dos heyst tsuzamen ⟨z-⟩ flegt ir tsoln fertsik lit?

257
00:13:34,264 --> 00:13:38,270
mir hobn beyde, in eyn tsimer hobn mir ge⟨UNK⟩ gelebt UNK ⟨mir⟩ geven un...

258
00:13:38,500 --> 00:13:42,881
un in, bay aykh in di dire iz geven vaser-leytung, tualet, tsu...?

259
00:13:42,224 --> 00:13:44,090
s'iz geven altseding.

260
00:13:44,170 --> 00:13:45,497
ineveynik, ya?

261
00:13:44,867 --> 00:13:46,790
alts iz geven in moyer, ya.

262
00:13:46,313 --> 00:13:47,994
un a vane iz oykh geven?

263
00:13:48,388 --> 00:13:49,867
a vane iz nit geven.

264
00:13:50,076 --> 00:13:54,561
dos iz der moyer avu s'iz antkegn ČARN⟨AS⟩, dortn oyf KALVIŲ,

265
00:13:54,561 --> 00:13:57,880
punkt antkegn i- in dem moyer hob ikh gelebt,

266
00:13:58,581 --> 00:14:03,380
vu dortn iz geven ČARN⟨AS⟩, MEMORIAL'NAYA...

267
00:14:02,968 --> 00:14:05,982
a. vos dos hot shpeter geheysn ČARN⟨AS⟩ gas, ya?

268
00:14:05,260 --> 00:14:09,350
ya. frier geven KALVIŲ, nokh dem ČAR⟨UNK⟩.

269
00:14:10,562 --> 00:14:16,074
 un, i- ir fleg- ir flegt zikh dan, muzn banutsn tsayt fun tsayt mit a bod, ye?

270
00:14:16,382 --> 00:14:17,382
vi den?

271
00:14:17,447 --> 00:14:19,753
vu iz dan geven di bod? ir gedenkt?

272
00:14:19,390 --> 00:14:22,170
UNK ⟨oyf,⟩, LUKŠIO gas.

273
00:14:21,818 --> 00:14:24,714
a, mit di bod oyf LUKŠIO gas flegt ir zikh banutsn?

274
00:14:23,565 --> 00:14:25,160
ya, ya.

275
00:14:25,615 --> 00:14:26,858
zogt mir...

276
00:14:25,665 --> 00:14:27,560
s'iz geven a gas oyf,

277
00:14:27,560 --> 00:14:33,051
oyf P-, PERGAL⟨UNK⟩ PERGALĖS KRANTINĖ. vi hot er dan geheysn?...

278
00:14:32,550 --> 00:14:33,911
MINDAUGO efsher?

279
00:14:34,052 --> 00:14:34,788
ha?

280
00:14:35,082 --> 00:14:37,337
dortn iz geven a,

281
00:14:37,478 --> 00:14:40,594
dortn iz nokh dem gevorn, a zeyf-, fabrik.

282
00:14:40,127 --> 00:14:41,353
fabrik, ya?

283
00:14:41,190 --> 00:14:42,860
dortn iz geven a bod frier.

284
00:14:42,945 --> 00:14:46,264
 efsher gede- kent ir mir zogn,

285
00:14:46,759 --> 00:14:53,115
ayer lebn hot zikh a bisl gebitn, in fertsiktn yor ⟨ve- z-⟩ ven do zaynen in, aray- arayn di rusn?

286
00:14:54,589 --> 00:14:58,350
nu, s'hot zikh gebitn mit ot vos:

287
00:14:58,350 --> 00:15:01,046
der b- der balebos hot zikh zeyer,

288
00:15:01,153 --> 00:15:03,847
er hot zeyer ibergelebt. er hot zikh zeyer dershrokn,

289
00:15:04,005 --> 00:15:07,627
m'vet bay im natsyonalizirn altsding, ⟨bay im veln mir⟩ alts tsunemen,

290
00:15:08,038 --> 00:15:11,424
m'vet... un er vet blaybn, vi me zogt, vi er shteyt un er geyt.

291
00:15:11,970 --> 00:15:16,270
nu, glaykh hot zikh genumen sh-, organizirn arteln.

292
00:15:16,527 --> 00:15:19,592
mir zaynen ale avek arbetn in artel zaynen mir avek arbetn.

293
00:15:19,817 --> 00:15:23,054
gearbet hob ikh oyf, Vilner gas iz geven

294
00:15:23,054 --> 00:15:26,696
⟨KONFEKTSION⟩, artel ⟨KONFEKTSION⟩.

295
00:15:28,040 --> 00:15:28,930
der bal-...

296
00:15:28,080 --> 00:15:29,514
vos hot der artel gemakht?

297
00:15:30,381 --> 00:15:32,327
dortn flegt men makhn,

298
00:15:32,327 --> 00:15:34,644
oykh farsheydene kleyder neyen.

299
00:15:35,038 --> 00:15:37,640
di familye, der balebos iz geven Khasman.

300
00:15:38,228 --> 00:15:40,146
d- er iz geven a balebos?

301
00:15:40,320 --> 00:15:47,310
nu, er iz geven a balebos, nor azoy vi er iz geven a guter mentsh, hot men im nokh dem ibergelozn onfirn mit di ⟨f-⟩ masterskaye.

302
00:15:47,087 --> 00:15:49,173
vi, als shoyn a direktor mistome?

303
00:15:49,028 --> 00:15:53,645
nu, ikh veys nit vos dan hot zikh gerufn. er iz geven der onfirer mi- mit di ale...

304
00:15:54,360 --> 00:15:55,181
ir z-...

305
00:15:54,410 --> 00:15:59,450
keyner, m'hot oyf im keyner zikh nit ge- baklogt. ⟨er hot⟩ UNK ⟨mit di⟩ arbeter, dos,

306
00:15:59,450 --> 00:16:02,421
hot men im ibergelozn, onfirn mit di shnayderay.

307
00:16:02,578 --> 00:16:08,124
ir zayt, ir zayt geven tsufridn az ir geyt a- avek fun Kremern tsu Khasmanen?

308
00:16:08,873 --> 00:16:11,735
nu, mir hobn zeyer gut fardint in di arteln.

309
00:16:12,332 --> 00:16:15,988
bay, in di, in di artel iz nokh geven di fardinst nokh hekher?

310
00:16:15,172 --> 00:16:16,720
nokh hekher, ya.

311
00:16:16,737 --> 00:16:18,705
efsher gedenkt ir vifl umgefer?

312
00:16:18,964 --> 00:16:21,219
vi nor s'zaynen arayn dan di rusn,

313
00:16:21,495 --> 00:16:24,577
hobn mir genumen neyen far di rusn

314
00:16:24,921 --> 00:16:27,820
shineln, zeyere zakhn,

315
00:16:27,820 --> 00:16:30,973
un zey zaynen gekumen, di rusn, mit pek mit gelt.

316
00:16:31,114 --> 00:16:34,112
zey flegn nit fregn ⟨afile; me fleg oyfneyen⟩ zey

317
00:16:34,202 --> 00:16:37,337
a kostyum, a tikhl, a por hoyzn, a shinel,

318
00:16:37,337 --> 00:16:42,570
flegn zey a vorf gebn ⟨a, vi tsu a kurve⟩ gelt un,... ⟨mir hobn⟩ zeyer gut fardint.

319
00:16:42,285 --> 00:16:46,835
efsher gedenkt ir velkhe gelt zaynen shoyn dan geven? z- flegt er tsoln mit rubls tsu nokh mit litn?

320
00:16:45,451 --> 00:16:46,930
tshervo-...

321
00:16:46,930 --> 00:16:49,570
neyn, keyn, rubl, rubls...

322
00:16:49,963 --> 00:16:52,050
tshervonts⟨UNK⟩...

323
00:16:51,482 --> 00:16:53,838
 a. rusishe shoyn gelt, nit keyn litvishe.

324
00:16:52,613 --> 00:16:54,370
ye, rusishe gelt.

325
00:16:54,958 --> 00:16:58,280
rusishe gelt iz shoyn geven; litn ⟨zaynen shoyn⟩ nit gegangen dan.

326
00:16:59,413 --> 00:17:03,940
un, azoy iz dos, g- ayer lebn gegangen biz der milkhome?

327
00:17:04,122 --> 00:17:07,744
azoy iz gegangen der lebn biz der milkhome, ya.

328
00:17:09,268 --> 00:17:13,278
efsher kent ir itster dertseyln, ir gedenkt dem ershtn tog fun milkhome?

329
00:17:12,896 --> 00:17:17,818
nu, itster azoy: dem f- der tog farn ershtn tog,

330
00:17:18,651 --> 00:17:20,450
dos iz geven shabes,

331
00:17:20,710 --> 00:17:27,921
un s'iz geven zeyer a fayner tog, azoy vi itster, vi haynt. hobn mir zikh gehat ale tsuzamengeredt... geven a groyse, khaveyrim hob ikh gehat zeyer fil...

332
00:17:27,921 --> 00:17:31,372
hobn mir zikh opgeredt az mir veln forn oyf morgn in Katshergin.

333
00:17:31,372 --> 00:17:34,120
nu, ⟨zikh⟩ farbrengen dem tog, opruen zikh.

334
00:17:37,652 --> 00:17:39,148
opruen zikh...

335
00:17:39,188 --> 00:17:43,097
nu, hobn mir opgeredt az mir veln geyn ale tsum damfer,

336
00:17:43,356 --> 00:17:45,260
un dortn veln mir zikh ale zetsn

337
00:17:45,260 --> 00:17:48,345
un mir veln avekforn un mir veln dortn farbrengen dem tog tsayt.

338
00:17:48,368 --> 00:17:54,015
ikh bin avekgegangen, s'iz geven a zeyger shoyn akht in der fri, iz dortn geven mayne ale khaveyrim, bakante.

339
00:17:54,358 --> 00:18:02,486
un dortn zaynen oykh geven rusishe ofitsern, politrukn, oykh geforn, s'iz geven zeyer a sheyner tog, zaynen geforn ale in Katshergin.

340
00:18:02,509 --> 00:18:09,168
dos iz geven a geveynlekhe zakh in, fertsiktn, eyn un fertsiktn yor, az mentshn flegn forn shabes in Katshergin, in Kalatove?

341
00:18:09,613 --> 00:18:11,160
s'iz geven a geveynlekhe zakh.

342
00:18:11,487 --> 00:18:14,484
geven ⟨a ge- vayle, nu, m'hot shoyn⟩ nit gedarft hobn keyn groyse gelt oyf derayn.

343
00:18:15,553 --> 00:18:19,720
nu, mir zaynen shoyn gezesn ale oyfn, oyfn

344
00:18:19,720 --> 00:18:22,150
damfer UNK parakhod UNK, vi me zogt,...

345
00:18:21,460 --> 00:18:22,702
 damfer, yo.

346
00:18:22,150 --> 00:18:22,955
damfer.

347
00:18:23,535 --> 00:18:27,312
nu, opgezesn umgefer a fuftsn minut un mit a mol

348
00:18:27,312 --> 00:18:29,334
mir zeen az s'flien onet...

349
00:18:29,948 --> 00:18:31,140
eroplanen?

350
00:18:30,360 --> 00:18:31,798
eroplanen, ye.

351
00:18:32,040 --> 00:18:33,637
un zey hobn genumen bashisn

352
00:18:34,690 --> 00:18:35,916
dem erodrom.

353
00:18:37,542 --> 00:18:41,200
un s'zitsn lebn un- lebn mir zitsn di, ofitsern.

354
00:18:41,200 --> 00:18:48,420
freg ikh eynem, "vos, vos, vos kumt do for?" "a," zogt er, "s'iz manevers bay undz." manevers.

355
00:18:48,375 --> 00:18:51,794
ir hot, d- mitn ofitsir, vos far a shprakh hot ir geredt?

356
00:18:51,970 --> 00:18:53,070
oyf rusish.

357
00:18:52,678 --> 00:18:54,730
ir hot shoyn dan gekent reydn rusish?

358
00:18:55,075 --> 00:19:02,156
ikh bin shoyn geven opgegebn, in armey. hot men undz geshikt glaykh ⟨ru-⟩ oyf, oyf kursn rusish zikh lernen.

359
00:19:02,483 --> 00:19:06,965
nu, ikh hob nit gekent perfekt, nor hob ikh, fleg ikh shoyn kenen umgefer zikh tsuzamenreydn mit zey.

360
00:19:07,191 --> 00:19:10,037
ikh hob gefregt... lebn mir iz ge⟨zes⟩n a politruk.

361
00:19:10,178 --> 00:19:13,834
⟨kh'hob nokh⟩ DAZHE zayn, zayn tshin nit gevust vos se batayt.

362
00:19:14,177 --> 00:19:17,309
nu, hot er mir gezogt, "s'iz, dos iz manevers, dos iz keyn zakh nit."

363
00:19:17,620 --> 00:19:21,124
mir zitsn vayter. der, der damfer fort nokh nit opet.

364
00:19:21,163 --> 00:19:23,452
s'iz avek nokh a fuftsn minut,

365
00:19:23,627 --> 00:19:29,274
ongefloygn a tsveyte e⟨k⟩skadrilye mit eroplanen, un m'hot genumen vider bombardirn, vider klapn.

366
00:19:29,905 --> 00:19:32,464
mit a mol iz gevorn oyfn, a panik iz gevorn,

367
00:19:32,487 --> 00:19:37,172
un m'hot geheysn alemen loyfn vos gikher fun, funem, fun, damfer.

368
00:19:37,853 --> 00:19:40,952
loyfndik... ikh hob dan gelebt oyf KALVIŲ gas...

369
00:19:41,110 --> 00:19:43,095
loyfndik aheym

370
00:19:46,037 --> 00:19:51,860
hob ikh gehert, s'iz geven, in eyn ort iz geven ofn a fentster, hob ikh gehert vi s'hot geredt Molotov.

371
00:19:52,332 --> 00:19:54,725
hot er gezogt az s'hot zikh ongefangen di krig;

372
00:19:54,725 --> 00:19:56,606
di daytshn zaynen ongefaln

373
00:19:56,606 --> 00:19:59,440
n- nit UNK nit, gen-...

374
00:19:59,352 --> 00:20:00,628
nit gevart?

375
00:20:00,162 --> 00:20:06,010
nit gevart. nu, V OBSHCHEM, nit, nit gevart zaynen ongefaln oyf Rusland....

376
00:20:05,258 --> 00:20:08,424
dos iz geven oyf rusish hot ir dos gehert di AUditsye fun, durkh a...?

377
00:20:07,790 --> 00:20:12,289
oyf rusish ⟨geven⟩. kh'hob farshtanen, vayle s'iz geven ofn der fentster UNK ⟨ikh bin⟩ grade farbaygegangen.

378
00:20:13,206 --> 00:20:16,536
ikh bin ts- gekumen tsu loyfn aheym. in shtub iz keyner nit geven.

379
00:20:16,536 --> 00:20:18,037
kler ikh, "vos zol ikh do ton?"

380
00:20:18,037 --> 00:20:21,350
mayn shvester hot gelebt, eyne, oyf ITALIJOS gas.

381
00:20:20,682 --> 00:20:22,332
velkhe, antshuldikt?

382
00:20:21,680 --> 00:20:22,797
Tsherne.

383
00:20:22,332 --> 00:20:23,932
Tsherne hot gelebt oyf I-...

384
00:20:23,263 --> 00:20:25,130
gelebt oyf ITALIJOS dray.

385
00:20:26,790 --> 00:20:28,016
⟨ya, redt!⟩

386
00:20:28,090 --> 00:20:31,189
di tsveyte hot gelebt oyf,

387
00:20:31,245 --> 00:20:34,749
dan hot zikh gerufn, ⟨ŠEŠIOLIKTA⟩ VASARIO,

388
00:20:35,380 --> 00:20:36,808
di tsveyte shvester.

389
00:20:37,067 --> 00:20:42,714
azoy vi zi iz geven, Tsherne, nenter tsu mir... ITALIJOS fun KALVIŲ iz nit vayt... bin ikh gelofn tsu ir.

390
00:20:42,771 --> 00:20:44,317
avekgelofn tsu ir,

391
00:20:44,340 --> 00:20:47,000
di shtub iz geven farshlosn; keyner iz shoyn nit geven in shtub.

392
00:20:47,462 --> 00:20:51,703
un ir man, Tsherne's... hot shoyn khasene ge-, khasene gehat...

393
00:20:51,703 --> 00:20:56,200
hot gehat oyf UGNIAGESIŲ gas a masterskaye in a keler. er flegt makhn...

394
00:20:55,157 --> 00:20:56,653
vi hot geheysn ir man?

395
00:20:57,047 --> 00:20:59,251
vi hot geheysn der man, Tsherne's?

396
00:20:59,000 --> 00:21:01,840
Abrashe. Avrom Kvartovski.

397
00:21:00,241 --> 00:21:01,241
⟨u-...⟩

398
00:21:01,502 --> 00:21:02,677
Kvartovski?

399
00:21:02,369 --> 00:21:03,640
Kvartovski, ya.

400
00:21:04,067 --> 00:21:06,626
un der Kvartovski hot gehat a varshtat, ya?

401
00:21:06,126 --> 00:21:10,860
varkshtat. er flegt makhn ayzerne betn, farsheydene ayzerne z-, zakhn.

402
00:21:12,876 --> 00:21:19,100
nu, s'iz geven farshlosn di shtub. nu, hob ikh a kler gegebn, me darf geyn dortn vu er hot, vu er arbet.

403
00:21:19,100 --> 00:21:21,411
ikh bin avek oyf UGNIAGESIŲ gas.

404
00:21:21,411 --> 00:21:26,437
dos iz umgefer punkt antkegn di MUZYKAL'NAYA SHKO- di MUZYKAL'NAYA...

405
00:21:26,595 --> 00:21:27,736
shul, ya?

406
00:21:27,234 --> 00:21:28,234
shul, ya.

407
00:21:28,705 --> 00:21:30,707
dan iz dos oykhet geven a muzik-shul?

408
00:21:30,713 --> 00:21:31,348
ya.

409
00:21:32,434 --> 00:21:38,059
ikh bin arayn in keler, hob ikh shoyn gefunen dortn ful: geven dortn mayn sh-, shvester, mayn bruder,

410
00:21:38,059 --> 00:21:43,433
un dem, dem, di shvester's man's, dray shvester, zayn muter.

411
00:21:43,433 --> 00:21:45,219
geven zeyer fil dortn geven.

412
00:21:45,377 --> 00:21:46,755
in a keler, ya?

413
00:21:46,255 --> 00:21:47,464
in a keler, ya.

414
00:21:48,130 --> 00:21:51,920
 dortn geven mayn bruder. der bruder yinger far mir iz geven.

415
00:21:51,418 --> 00:21:53,268
vi iz der nomen fun dem bruder geven?

416
00:21:52,768 --> 00:21:53,640
Meyer.

417
00:21:53,882 --> 00:21:56,120
er iz geven yinger far mir iz er geven.

418
00:21:56,430 --> 00:22:00,237
hot er glaykh genumen reydn tsu mir, "lomir forn in Zarasay."

419
00:22:01,527 --> 00:22:04,060
nu, er vil, hot gevelt zikh zayn mit di eltern.

420
00:22:06,015 --> 00:22:07,814
Tsherne iz geven oyf der tsayt,

421
00:22:08,007 --> 00:22:10,380
hot nit gekent, zi iz geven in di letste monatn.

422
00:22:11,280 --> 00:22:18,395
 z-, zayn, zayn, ir man's a shvester iz geven a khasene-gehate far a politruk,

423
00:22:19,060 --> 00:22:22,446
hot zi moyre gehat, az di daytshn veln kumen, vet men ⟨ir di ershte⟩ derhargenen.

424
00:22:22,705 --> 00:22:25,466
iz ikh, zi un der bruder,

425
00:22:25,506 --> 00:22:28,233
hobn mir opgeredt az mir veln loyfn,

426
00:22:29,033 --> 00:22:31,929
aroysgeyn fun keler un loyfn tsum ban;

427
00:22:32,003 --> 00:22:33,752
efsher vet undz gelingen tsu antloyfn.

428
00:22:33,910 --> 00:22:35,372
un forn oyf Zarasay?

429
00:22:35,682 --> 00:22:38,679
nu, oyf Zarasay, vi me zogt, vu di oygn veln trogn.

430
00:22:39,630 --> 00:22:44,771
mir zaynen a- vi nor mir zaynen aroys fun keler, hot men undz, oyf undz geefnt a fayer fun di MUZYKAL'Ne shul,

431
00:22:44,895 --> 00:22:46,407
a URAGANNe fayer.

432
00:22:46,515 --> 00:22:47,769
undz iz gelungen

433
00:22:47,769 --> 00:22:49,195
zikh tsu fardreyen

434
00:22:49,195 --> 00:22:50,402
oyf KANTO

435
00:22:50,402 --> 00:22:52,551
un mir zaynen aroys lebedikerheyt.

436
00:22:53,113 --> 00:23:02,422
mir zaynen opgegangen umgefer a, nu, nit vayt fun TSENTRAL'NAYA POCHTA un s'iz gelegn gehargete soldatn, tsivile ⟨mentshn⟩ gehargete, ⟨zaynen⟩ gelegn oyfn, oyf LAISVĖS ALĖJA.

437
00:23:03,930 --> 00:23:05,698
mir zaynen tsugegangen

438
00:23:05,698 --> 00:23:07,552
nit vayt fun SOBOR.

439
00:23:09,988 --> 00:23:12,715
tsugelofn tsu undz dray soldatn,

440
00:23:13,617 --> 00:23:17,100
Ka- di Kalmik⟨er⟩ UNK vi, vi zogt men, mit di shmole eygelekh.

441
00:23:16,688 --> 00:23:18,116
nit keyn rusn, ya?

442
00:23:17,730 --> 00:23:18,993
nit keyn rusn.

443
00:23:19,506 --> 00:23:20,850
mit biksn,

444
00:23:21,177 --> 00:23:23,449
un zey heysn undz oyfheybn di hent,

445
00:23:23,472 --> 00:23:28,241
un zey zogn, "ir hot geshosn in undz; mir veln aykh shoyn, aykh alemen dershisn. ir hot in undz geshosn."

446
00:23:28,821 --> 00:23:33,472
hob ikh genumen tsu zey zikh betn un veynen: "mir zaynen yidn; mir loyfn punkt vi ir!"

447
00:23:33,900 --> 00:23:41,592
gefaln oyf di kni tsu zey. kam-kam zikh, hob⟨n mir zey b-⟩ ayngeredt un zey hobn gezogt, "loyft shnel fun danen un farshvindt fun undzere oygn,

448
00:23:41,592 --> 00:23:42,939
⟨mir zoln aykh⟩ mer nit zen!"

449
00:23:43,654 --> 00:23:48,103
azoy zaynen mir gel- tsugelofn biz ⟨di⟩ AVTOBUSn stantsye.

450
00:23:48,632 --> 00:23:51,660
⟨BUSn⟩ stantsye. ongeforn

451
00:23:51,720 --> 00:23:55,696
Royte Armeyer mit, UNK ⟨gerufn⟩ TACHANKes.

452
00:23:55,804 --> 00:23:57,510
koyln-varfers azelkhe.

453
00:23:57,188 --> 00:23:57,722
nu.

454
00:23:58,622 --> 00:24:03,003
ongeforn. zaynen dortn gezesn fir kome- fir ofitsern.

455
00:24:03,330 --> 00:24:10,355
zi hot derzen az dortn zitst ofitsern. azoy vi, zi hot gez-... ir man iz geven a politruk, di vos iz gelofn mit undz,

456
00:24:10,355 --> 00:24:11,981
dem shvoger's shvester...

457
00:24:12,460 --> 00:24:17,904
iz zi tsugelofn tsu zey un gevizn az ir man iz a VOENNer, a politruk, hobn zey ⟨ir⟩ ayngezetst oykh in vogn,

458
00:24:17,910 --> 00:24:22,330
un mir hobn genumen zogn zey, "gey avek, gey avek! s'iz far aykh keyn ort nito."

459
00:24:22,330 --> 00:24:25,768
ikh bin ⟨geblibn dortn⟩ mitn bruder aleyn un zi iz shoyn avekgeforn mit zey.

460
00:24:26,432 --> 00:24:30,307
opgegangen umgefer nokh a tsvantsik, draysik meter,

461
00:24:30,499 --> 00:24:33,024
m'hot vider genumen shisn; fun vanen veysn mir nit.

462
00:24:33,891 --> 00:24:37,023
mayn bruder iz arayngelofn in eyn hoyf, ikh in a tsveytn hoyf.

463
00:24:37,350 --> 00:24:40,010
ikh bin dort opgeven umgefer a tsvantsik minut.

464
00:24:40,033 --> 00:24:42,187
s'iz gevorn a bisele ruiker.

465
00:24:42,396 --> 00:24:45,022
ikh gey aroyset. der bruder iz nito.

466
00:24:46,142 --> 00:24:49,376
nu, kler ikh, vos tut men vayter?

467
00:24:49,753 --> 00:24:52,126
bashlosn, me darf geyn vayter. ⟨vu vel ikh geyn...?⟩

468
00:24:52,386 --> 00:24:58,354
azoy bin ikh avek vayter, ⟨d-⟩ tsug⟨et-⟩, tsugeyendik tsu nokh a kompanye, nokh, nokh khaveyrim yidishe,

469
00:24:58,360 --> 00:24:59,872
un mir zaynen gegangen.

470
00:25:00,840 --> 00:25:02,622
mir zaynen gegangen

471
00:25:03,726 --> 00:25:06,820
biz U- biz Vilkomir.

472
00:25:07,033 --> 00:25:08,169
biz Vilkomir?

473
00:25:07,742 --> 00:25:08,461
ya.

474
00:25:08,169 --> 00:25:10,638
dos iz dray un zekhtsik kilometer fun Kovne.

475
00:25:09,733 --> 00:25:11,634
ya. zaynen mir gegangen tsu fus.

476
00:25:11,640 --> 00:25:13,423
⟨bi-⟩ avek biz Vilkomir,

477
00:25:13,446 --> 00:25:18,232
un ⟨nokh⟩ umetum hobn ⟨mir nokh⟩ getrofn alts di rusishe s- di rusishe armey hobn mir nokh alts getrofn.

478
00:25:18,424 --> 00:25:22,080
nu, zaynen zey shoyn kontik⟨, nokh zeyer gang,⟩ zaynen zey shoyn gelofn fun danen.

479
00:25:22,187 --> 00:25:24,746
zey hobn keyn vidershtand kimat vi nit geshtelt.

480
00:25:25,731 --> 00:25:30,956
far, ni- hinter, nit vayt fun Vilkomir zaynen mir arayn in a vald

481
00:25:31,047 --> 00:25:32,604
zikh opruen dortn,

482
00:25:32,604 --> 00:25:38,207
un mir flegn avekshteln oyfn, oyfn veg pos-, nu, vakh, me zol zen vi di lage iz,

483
00:25:38,207 --> 00:25:40,625
un di iberike flegn lign in vald un zikh ruen.

484
00:25:41,357 --> 00:25:44,670
ikh bin geshtanen lebn veg mit eynem

485
00:25:44,670 --> 00:25:46,126
a khaver mayner.

486
00:25:46,369 --> 00:25:47,780
mir gibn a kuk...

487
00:25:48,175 --> 00:25:50,396
⟨nu, s'⟩hot gemuzt zayn mistome a zeyger

488
00:25:51,077 --> 00:25:52,876
tsvelf, eyns bay tog...

489
00:25:53,153 --> 00:25:55,037
mir gibn a kuk fun vaytn:

490
00:25:55,043 --> 00:25:57,416
vi es geyt di veg, iz in di zaytn

491
00:25:58,536 --> 00:26:00,251
geyen tsu undz soldatn.

492
00:26:00,240 --> 00:26:01,297
rusishe?

493
00:26:01,573 --> 00:26:03,457
ikh hob, mir hobn nit gevust ver zey zaynen.

494
00:26:03,531 --> 00:26:08,840
hob ikh zikh derfreyt. zog ikh, "s'zaynen nokh, di rusn zaynen nokh do bay undz. s'zaynen nokh do di rusn. n⟨i⟩to vos moyre tsu hobn."

495
00:26:09,066 --> 00:26:11,287
vi zey zaynen tsugegangen nenter,

496
00:26:11,293 --> 00:26:13,154
hobn mir derzen az zey zaynen shoyn daytshn.

497
00:26:13,154 --> 00:26:15,680
dos iz gegangen a RAZVEDKe. UNK

498
00:26:14,635 --> 00:26:16,704
a oysshpirer, ye? oysshpirer.

499
00:26:15,780 --> 00:26:17,710
ye, oysshpirer, oysshpirer, ye.

500
00:26:17,925 --> 00:26:21,446
fun beyde zaytn. s'zaynen geven umgefer a fuftsn, tsvantsik man.

501
00:26:22,043 --> 00:26:24,095
glaykh zaynen tsugegangen tsu undz.

502
00:26:24,861 --> 00:26:28,700
nu, KUL'TU-, V OBSHCHEM, geredt UNK...

503
00:26:27,223 --> 00:26:28,347
heflekh.

504
00:26:29,215 --> 00:26:33,276
geredt KUL'TURNe: "ver zayt ir? vos, vu zaynen di rusn?"

505
00:26:33,433 --> 00:26:38,557
hobn mir gezogt, "in der fri hobn mir nokh zey gezen. in der fri hot zikh nokh gehert a shiseray, un itster iz shtil gevorn."

506
00:26:38,918 --> 00:26:41,949
zey hobn undz glaykh ba- ba- gezukht di keshenes,

507
00:26:41,955 --> 00:26:44,610
gefunen dortn meserlekh, ZA- di,

508
00:26:44,610 --> 00:26:49,053
 ZAZHIGALKes, hobn zey tsugenumen un zey hobn zikh umgekert tsurik un avek tsurik.

509
00:26:49,819 --> 00:26:52,110
nu, mir hobn shoyn nit gehat vayter vu tsu geyn.

510
00:26:52,110 --> 00:26:54,183
UNK I VSЁ.

511
00:26:54,257 --> 00:26:56,175
⟨farn⟩ UNK far undz UNK vayter.

512
00:26:57,092 --> 00:26:59,170
a zeyger zeks in ovnt

513
00:26:59,170 --> 00:27:01,170
hot genumen geyn di gantse armey.

514
00:27:00,889 --> 00:27:01,929
daytshishe?

515
00:27:01,730 --> 00:27:02,820
daytshishe armey, ye.

516
00:27:02,931 --> 00:27:09,337
efsher gedenkt ir, vos far a tog fun der milkhome iz dos geven az ir zayt, der- az ir hot derzen di daytshn? der tsveyter tsu der driter?

517
00:27:08,494 --> 00:27:10,700
dos iz geven mon- der montik.

518
00:27:10,575 --> 00:27:12,037
der tsveyter tog shoyn?

519
00:27:11,537 --> 00:27:12,881
tsveyter tog.

520
00:27:13,714 --> 00:27:15,210
un efsher der driter...

521
00:27:15,638 --> 00:27:17,387
ir flegt geyn durkh nakht dan?

522
00:27:17,646 --> 00:27:19,361
ir zayt gegangen durkh nakht?

523
00:27:19,502 --> 00:27:25,600
mir flegn bay nakht geyn un bay tog geyn. bay tog flegn mir merstn teyl, zikh opruen, un geyn flegn mir bay nakht.

524
00:27:27,012 --> 00:27:31,005
 derfar UNK shver gedenken tsu der tsveyter tog iz dos geven, tsu der driter.

525
00:27:31,045 --> 00:27:32,895
dos hot gemuzt zayn der driter tog.

526
00:27:33,171 --> 00:27:34,616
gemuzt zayn der driter tog.

527
00:27:34,470 --> 00:27:36,506
ven di daytshn hobn aykh ongeyogt.

528
00:27:37,542 --> 00:27:41,451
vayle... nu, nokh dem, shpeter vel ikh es efsher der- dervisn.

529
00:27:43,077 --> 00:27:46,564
nu, nokh dem, az di daytshn zaynen shoyn gegangen oyf Kovne, di gantse armey,

530
00:27:47,262 --> 00:27:51,795
hobn mir zikh umgekert. mir zaynen gegangen tsuzamen mit zey zaynen mir gegangen mit di armey oyf Kovne.

531
00:27:52,324 --> 00:27:56,340
zey zaynen durkhgeforn. zey hobn gezen az ale zaynen mir di, nu,

532
00:27:56,678 --> 00:27:58,916
antlofene fun, fun di heymen,

533
00:27:58,922 --> 00:28:01,129
shmutsike, hungerike.

534
00:28:01,129 --> 00:28:05,196
flegn zikh opshteln andere ki- di ki- di kikhn zeyere

535
00:28:05,196 --> 00:28:09,036
un DAZHE undz gebn broyt mit kashe opesn mit alts.

536
00:28:09,036 --> 00:28:13,850
eynike flegn undz fartshepenen: "fort in, Palestine. vos tut ir ⟨do⟩ UNK?"

537
00:28:13,452 --> 00:28:14,543
ver,...?

538
00:28:14,346 --> 00:28:15,352
fun di daytshn.

539
00:28:15,055 --> 00:28:16,956
un zey hobn gevust az ir zayt yidn?

540
00:28:16,843 --> 00:28:20,000
nu, zey hobn gezen az, yidishe nezer.

541
00:28:19,678 --> 00:28:22,720
di daytshn hobn gekent untersheydn, ver iz a yid, ver...?

542
00:28:21,564 --> 00:28:23,450
ye, zey hobn⟨,⟩ untergesheydt.

543
00:28:24,184 --> 00:28:26,068
nu, azoy zaynen mir gekumen

544
00:28:26,378 --> 00:28:29,760
umgefer nit vayt fun Murave.

545
00:28:30,816 --> 00:28:32,278
dos iz geven,

546
00:28:33,432 --> 00:28:35,889
⟨gemuzt⟩ zayn in der fri, a zeyger tsen, elf,

547
00:28:36,452 --> 00:28:39,348
gekumen in Murave. geze- oysgezen hobn mir strashne.

548
00:28:39,591 --> 00:28:40,750
shreklekh, ya?

549
00:28:40,360 --> 00:28:44,050
shreklekh: shmutsik, hungerik.

550
00:28:44,383 --> 00:28:46,773
geyt undz on eyne a eltere froy,

551
00:28:47,877 --> 00:28:56,420
zogt tsu undz, "geyt nit in Kovne, vayl in Slabodke iz geven a pogrom. m'hot oysgekoylet zeyer fil mentshn in, oysgeharget in Slabod-..."

